data.description: Rare opportunity to make this newer construction Midtown home all yours! Built in 2019 with beautiful finishes throughout. This 3 bed, 2 full bath home has beautiful hardwood floors, granite counters and large closets throughout for all your storage needs.  The open living room and kitchen area provide a wonderful space for entertaining.  Prime location close to Mother Road Market, TU, Downtown, breweries, the Pearl District, Cherry Street and easy highway access.
